IMHO, zend isn't very simple. Still very much in the works.

This is my customization of a starter 'guestbook' application
that I found on the zend framework website. I re-tooled it to just be a
generic post app. the changes that I want to make are forcing
me to get into the nitty gritty of the zf. it's how i learn. 